lead_paragraph: Joe Burns had planned to catch a few waves to fill the extra time in his schedule after being omitted from Australia's test squad against South Africa but the opening batsman has had to put the surfboard away due to a surprise recall for Hobart.

headline.print_headline: Batsman Burns' 'Surfari' Wiped Out by Test Recall
